race.description: 2025 Peter Kittle Toyota Gawler Gold Cup H Pr1 Div
race.comment: KISAUNI (6) is having his first start around this course. In the money last start when second (30.54) at Angle Park over 530m. Has a strong record out of this box with seven wins and four minor placings from 15 starts. Sure to be about the mark. UNWORLDLY (4) hit the frame last time at Geelong but the start prior rocketed around 515m at Sandown in 29.58. Top win two back and can measure up again. PEAKY BOO (1) was a last start winner (30.67) from Box 3 at Angle Park. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Deserves serious consideration again.  Something for the Multiples: NOLA KEEPING (3)
